Alembic is a database migration tool for SQLAlchemy.

## Creating Migrations

Create a new migration:
```bash
alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description"
```

Apply migrations:
```bash
alembic upgrade head
```

Rollback one migration:
```bash
alembic downgrade -1
```

View current version:
```bash
alembic current
```

View history:
```bash
alembic history
```
